                    "Title": "峡江 (出生地)",
                    "Detail": "<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"62b365f2604247deaf9ee44f51f1bc2f\");'><span id='62b365f2604247deaf9ee44f51f1bc2f_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1038&endYear=1060')\">1038-1060年</a>，1-23岁</div><div id='62b365f2604247deaf9ee44f51f1bc2f' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1038&endYear=1038')\">1038年7月28日</a>　文仲生，居乡。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1039&endYear=1041')\">1039-1041年</a>　居乡。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1042&endYear=1042')\">1042年</a>　居乡。父延之登榜进士。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1042&endYear=1042')\">1042年7月15日</a>　居乡。七月十五日，弟武仲生。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1043&endYear=1043')\">1043年</a>　居乡。文仲已能作诗。<span class='label'>作品：</span>莲实诗。<span class='inlineComment2'>（《独醒杂志》卷三：“孔经甫六七岁能作诗，其父司封君尝对客召经甫侍立。客命经甫为莲实诗，经甫立成。记其一联云：‘一茎青竹初出水，数个黄蜂占作巢。’语虽未工而比类亲切，客大奇之，经甫自此知名。”）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1044&endYear=1044')\">1044年6月9日</a>　居乡。六月九日，弟孔平仲生。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1045&endYear=1045')\">1045年</a>　居乡。父延之作《宋桂州瘗宜贼首级记》。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1046&endYear=1055')\">1046-1055年</a>　居乡。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1056&endYear=1056')\">1056年</a>　居乡。应乡举。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1057&endYear=1057')\">1057年</a>　居乡。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1058&endYear=1058')\">1058年</a>　居乡。再应乡举。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1059&endYear=1059')\">1059年</a>　居乡。弟武仲应乡举。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1060&endYear=1060')\">1060年</a>　居乡。<br /></div>"
